    "description": {
      "content": "Triton One's hosted Metaplex Digital Assets Standard (DAS) implementation, accessible through the same Solana RPC endpoint. Exposes compressed-NFT and SPL token introspection methods (getAsset, getAssetProof, searchAssets, getTokenAccounts, getTokenLargestAccounts, getAssetsByOwner/Creator/Authority, getNftEditions, etc.). Powered by Triton's Photon indexer infrastructure.\n\n\nContact Support:\n Name: Triton One Support\n Email: support@triton.one",
